description: This header file defines APIs for managing cable modem data models, including functions to get entry counts, retrieve entries, check updates, synchronize data via HAL API calls, and get parameter values for various cable modem related objects such as OFDM channels and OFDMA status. It appears to be part of a data model library for Cosa (Cisco Open Service Architecture).

methods.name: X_RDKCENTRAL_COM_CableModem_DsOfdmChan_GetEntryCount
methods.description: Retrieves the count of DS OFDM channels.

methods.name: X_RDKCENTRAL_COM_CableModem_DsOfdmChan_GetEntry
methods.description: Retrieves a specific DS OFDM channel entry by index.

methods.name: X_RDKCENTRAL_COM_CableModem_DsOfdmChan_IsUpdated
methods.description: Checks if DS OFDM channel table is updated.

methods.name: X_RDKCENTRAL_COM_CableModem_DsOfdmChan_Synchronize
methods.description: Synchronizes DS OFDM channel data via HAL API.

methods.name: X_RDKCENTRAL_COM_CableModem_DsOfdmChan_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves Ulong parameter value for DS OFDM channel.

methods.name: X_RDKCENTRAL_COM_CableModem_DsOfdmChan_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves string parameter value for DS OFDM channel.
